        "payload": [
          {
            "contentString": "{patientName} reports recent muscle pain as his main concern [SNOMED:M79.1]. He has not described a single clear traumatic event leading to the symptoms, and there is no documented prior hospitalization related to this complaint. He initially tried rest and reducing physical activity at home, but the muscle pain persisted [SNOMED:M79.1].\n\nHe has been functioning independently in daily life, though with some reduction in exercise and household activity because movement worsens his muscular discomfort [SNOMED:M79.1]. No additional comorbidity is directly supported by the provided evidence, so the remainder of his past medical history is unremarkable by available records. He presents now for outpatient assessment and symptomatic treatment of muscle pain [SNOMED:M79.1]."
          }
